comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T17:32:46.299Z",codex-root,"Lossless comparison against git show HEAD:CHANGELOG.md reported legacy_count=16, preserved_count=16, missing=[]."
  "2026-07-21T17:38:51.760Z",codex-root,"The first linked changelog check correctly failed after final pm comments and closures made the previously generated file stale. The required recovery is to regenerate after the last tracker mutation, then rerun the same check."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T17:22:25.139Z",codex-root,The original preamble stated that all notable changes are documented in CHANGELOG.md; generated ownership now makes closed pm items the source of truth while git history retains the exact hand-maintained snapshot.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T17:32:46.299Z",codex-root,"pm-changelog escapes nested Markdown link brackets in item titles, but retains the visible text and item link; the legacy PROJECT_HISTORY pointer remains present."
